    "ResNet50, ResNet101, and so on are examples of the classic ResNet.",
    "The issue of the network developing in a deeper direction without gradient explosion is resolved by forming the ResNet network.",
    "As is well known, DCNNs are excellent at extracting low-, medium-, and high-level characteristics from images.",
    "We can typically improve accuracy by adding additional layers.",
    "The activation function of each of the two dense layers in the residual module is the ReLU function."
